Enclosing class:
ClientSideFSM
static class ClientSideFSM.FetchRequest
extends EntityFSM.Request

FetchRequest is a request by a client Entity to connect to a server Entity. A FetchRequest object includes the following state information:

  • QoS -- quality of service requested from the server
  • ServerContact -- address of the server
